{"article_id":"FqdDCwoZo5kbyNVZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A former staffer for Democratic presidential candidate Joe Biden has reportedly filed a formal criminal complaint against her former boss with the Washington , D.C. police .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Tara Reade ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"who last month accused the former vice president and longtime senator of sexually assaulting her in 1993","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"while employed as one of his Senate staffers ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"told police","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that Biden \" assaulted her in a Senate corridor ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"shoving his hand under her skirt","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"and penetrating her with his fingers , \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Business Insider reported Saturday","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"while also noting","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that the \" statute of limitations for the alleged assault has passed . \"","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Reade told writer and podcast host Katie Halper about her allegations last month :","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"This is a story","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that @ ReadeAlexandra has been trying to tell","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"since it happened in 1993 .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"It ' s a story about sexual assault , retaliation and silencing .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"# meToo","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"https : //t.co/yHz3iFi9a5","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"- Katie Halper","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"( @ kthalps )","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"March 25 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" We were alone ,","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"and it was the strangest thing , \"","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Reade told Halper .","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"\" There was no , like , exchange really ,","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"he just had me up against the wall .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"His hands were on me and underneath my clothes .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"And then , he went ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"he went down my skirt","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"and then up inside it ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"and he penetrated me with his fingers...","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and um...","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"He was kissing me at the same time","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and he was saying something to me . \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" He got finished doing what he was doing","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and I ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"how I was pulled back","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and he said ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"' Come on man ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"I heard","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"you liked me. '","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"And that phrase stayed with me","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"because I kept thinking","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"what I might have said , \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"she continued .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"\" And I can ' t remember exactly","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"if he said","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"' I thought '","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"or if ' I heard. '","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"It ' s like he implied","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"that I had done this . \"","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Biden ' s campaign has vehemently denied the allegation .","depth":3},{"id":52,"text":"( RELATED :","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"Alyssa Milano Says","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Joe Biden Deserves ' Due Process ' In Sexual Assault Allegation )","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"\" Women have a right","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"to tell their story ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"and reporters have an obligation","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"to rigorously vet those claims .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"We encourage them to do so ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"because these accusations are false , \"","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"deputy campaign manager Kate Bedingfield said in a statement to Fox News .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":123,"left":112,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nucl